{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n527\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 7\u00d71 = 405 + 18 + 7 = 430\u2081\u2080\n\n408\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 0\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 324 + 0 + 8 = 332\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n430 \u00d7 332 = 430 \u00d7 (300 + 32) = 129,000 + 13,760 = 142,760\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n142760 \u00f7 9 = 15862 r 2\n15862 \u00f7 9 = 1762 r 4\n1762 \u00f7 9 = 195 r 7\n195 \u00f7 9 = 21 r 6\n21 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 3\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: 236742\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n236742\u2089 = 2\u00d759049 + 3\u00d76561 + 6\u00d7729 + 7\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 2\u00d71\n= 118098 + 19683 + 4374 + 567 + 36 + 2 = 142,760\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n236742", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 453}